{"tid":1472691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明明大家贏緊","createTime":"2019-08-14T15:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T15:58:16.000Z","uid":273593,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b59d9f5852e21fe3c809f1d18dc611745f7b389a","tid":1472691,"uid":273593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:46:42.000Z","msg":"以前失敗的抗爭方程式:<br />\n<br />\n聚人圍緒目標》設路障》堅守陣地》入夜少人被清場》tg放題+速龍》拉廿件<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新深水埗模式<br />\n<br />\n聚人燒街衣》 沒有路障》沒有陣地周圍燒》入夜更多街坊》tg準備好》全散番屋企睡覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />》tg放題》畀街坊屌走<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />》重覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>成功模式例子:</ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黃大仙，深水埗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>提一提大家，有幾樣嘢完全畀人忽視咗:</ins><br />\n<br />\n1. 速龍捉到人嘅次數永遠最高<br />\n<br />\n2. 佢哋喺100米範圍裏面捉人嘅成功率好高<br />\n<br />\n3. 某次速龍奔跑日就是因為示威者距離防線近200米<br />\n<br />\n4. 大部分被捕時間都係黑警衝前，撤退失敗<br />\n<br />\n5. 街坊對於催淚彈非常反感，迫黑警出咗催淚彈已經贏咗，因為大家都冇任何裝備、戰術可以擊潰黑警<br />\n<br />\n6. 黑警出唔到催淚彈，或者出完彈但冇示威者捉，就好似除咗褲射唔出，好損士氣。"},{"pid":"2838476f383b266ec69cec4198f7bcd681787e2b","tid":1472691,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:47:20.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"d4314dd1c426842332977a4596bde0bbd98bfe52","tid":1472691,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:47:38.000Z","msg":"啱"},{"pid":"223692ecc9b46003593cccccb7184519406bedc0","tid":1472691,"uid":273593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:47:57.000Z","msg":"再一次提醒大家 <br />\n<br />\n學堂訓練200米衝刺係基本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以只要有二百米範圍以上<br />\n<br />\n佢一追你就跑<br />\n<br />\n無敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e138ee7624b42015e1baf20841ca5fec42d9c8b","tid":1472691,"uid":224716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:47:59.000Z","msg":"[推上熱門] <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">核彈都唔割嘅真正原因</span></span><br />\n入黎睇下啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dEtzAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dEtzAS</a><br />\n一齊加油啊"},{"pid":"26f470ca4ecf7f480e3b7d2c260a9e7ec9e72103","tid":1472691,"uid":273593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:48:56.000Z","msg":"200米原則 = 速龍跑步日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29dec808edeb96ff3a14efbcce05815c8940bb34","tid":1472691,"uid":273593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:49:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f69339660bd5565a8ccfec36d95400344147d3fe","tid":1472691,"uid":273593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:51:02.000Z","msg":"撤退並唔係代表輸<br />\n<br />\n黑警都會佯撤退，引你哋上前，再衝出嚟拉人<br />\n<br />\n只不過大家調番轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d02b95fb788f01a792d52baf6ad16942cfe2dfa","tid":1472691,"uid":273593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:51:37.000Z","msg":"聚人燒街衣》 沒有路障》沒有陣地周圍燒》入夜更多街坊》<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">tg準備好》全散番屋企睡覺》tg放題》畀街坊屌走</span></span></strong>》重覆"},{"pid":"9f37668e8b1dbcb00b67f37329132e2fec685add","tid":1472691,"uid":273593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:52:05.000Z","msg":"又有狗入來負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02595c5e58fb38f16951cdc3889d6d19f8ba8f67","tid":1472691,"uid":273593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:53:04.000Z